Zype-CLI

== How to install

1. Build gem

gem build zype.gemspec

2. Install gem

gem install ./zype-1.0.0.gem

== How to use

1. Open irb

irb

2. Require gem

require 'zype'

3. Configure gem

# For a rails application add the following under:
# config/initializers/zype.rb

Zype.configure do |config|
  config.api_key = [your api key]
  config.host    = [host] # default: api.zype-core.com
  config.port    = [port] # default: 3000
  config.use_ssl = false  # default: false
end

4. Create a client

Zype::Client.new

3. Query zobjects

client.zobjects.all(zobject: 'team')
